<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. En un! meipi tawh A hung suk,
 Gilote zieka thah kha;
 Mithieng sang tam takin A zui,
 Zawh la A zuiten a sau.

[V2]
 Hallelujah (3)
 Isu vaihawm di'n A hung.

[V3]
 2. Mit chengin Amah mu tan tin,
 Lalna lauhum a kithuom;
 Amah musitte leh zuokte,
 A sunte leh khenden te'n.

[V4]
 Lungkham tawpin (3)
 Messie tak chuh hun mu'n au.

[V5]
 3. Pengkun lopi a hung gittieng,
 Lei leh van taimang ina;
 A mudah cheng chuh buoi untin,
 Zie ni chun sapna za'n au.

[V6]
 Vaihawm na ah (3)
 Hungin vaihawmna ah ti'n.

[V7]
 4. Tun tatna sawt a I kinep,
 En in, a hung kilang tai;
 Mi deihloh, A mi thiengthote'n,
 Amah vanah tuok unau.

[V8]
 Hallelujah (3)
 En un, Pathien ni a lang.

[V9]
 5. Amen, mitin in hun ho hen,
 Na kumsawt Lalchutphah ah;
 Lalpa, hatna, lopina la'n,
 Lalgam chuh Nanga hi hen.
 Hung kin mengin! (3)
 Hallelujah! hung kinin.</lyrics>
<title>LO! HE COMES</title>
<hymn_number>144</hymn_number>
</song>